            @"Error occurs when another game client or another process is already executing HackShield. Since the HackShield vr.3.1 has been improved to allow HackShield running in a multi-process environment%2C this does not occur in the newer version clients. (Value = 0x201)",
            @"Error occurs when the game client is executed in the Compatibility Mode provided by Windows XP. Game execution in Compatibility Mode is judged as a user with ill intentions%2C so program must be ended and restarted. (Value = 0x004)",
